<p><a href="https://www.facebook.com/machinelearningbasicvn/posts/449220955437741">Link gá»‘c</a>.</p>

<p>Trong bÃ i toÃ¡n Classification, pháº£i lÃ m nhÆ° tháº¿ nÃ o khi dá»¯ liá»‡u giá»¯a cÃ¡c class quÃ¡ chÃªnh lá»‡ch?</p>

<p>ÄÆ°á»ng link dÆ°á»›i Ä‘Ã¢y cÃ³ thá»ƒ mang láº¡i nhiá»u thÃ´ng tin cÃ³ Ã­ch cho báº¡n:</p>

<p><a href="https://www.kaggle.com/joparga3/in-depth-skewed-data-classif-93-recall-acc-now">In depth skewed data classification - Kaggle Kernel</a></p>

